musicInfo.song_name: Small Town Girl (From "Bachna Ae Haseeno") (feat. Ranbir Kapoor, Bipasha Basu)

latestPosts.caption:
Couldn’t recommend this one enough ⭐️🛁
Notes : 
-booked via @bookingcom , found that they had the best price 
- 10 minutes away from Ancient town which is where all the tailors , leather shops and the lantern boat ride is located. Overall great accessibly to most places you’d wanna see.
- 10 minute drive to Hidden beach and a little further for plenty of other beaches 
- Breakfast buffet included* which had so many options! 
- They have a lovely in-house spa and pool which I would highly recommend checking out 
- Highly recommend renting a scooter through the hotel which costs around 150,000 vitnamese dong per day!  Alternatively they also have free cycles available to use. 

Overall we truly enjoyed our stay so much here and can’t wait to be back ⭐️⭐️⭐️ 
.
.
